metadata.name: Heading Home
metadata.description:
The first piece in the Mistical Meta series, tells the story of a main character named Tristy who returns home, but things have changed a lot and he comes to meet his soulmate, Evra.
Tristy came from her journey together with several creatures who became her friends.
A new story has begun, the story of Tristy and Evra's journey in Mistical Meta and they will soon meet many creatures and environments with extreme shape.

OB3D 2022
4000 x 5000 px
300 dpi
